divs: sighting detailsi went outside to look at the stars about 7:55pm on tues night 3\12\13 in huntington beach. i hadn't been watching for more than 2 minutes when i saw a weird object pass overhead. it went from the south to north. i could see through it or it was cloaked somehow. it was a rectangle. i have no idea what it was. it was approx. 20,000 ft up and about thumb wide at arm's length. i have an aviation background about my entire life so i know what i'm looking at most of the time. this was amazing.
